  <p class="gd-lede">Iceland is the rare place where a single heliski season hands you two celestial spectacles: the Northern Lights in its dark early evenings and the midnight sun in its bright later ones. This is how to choose your week, then explore <a href="/packages">the packages</a> and <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
